==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Formication
<hw>For`mi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>formicatio</ets>, fr. <ets>formicare</ets> to creep like an ant, to
feel as if ants were crawling on one's self, fr. <ets>formica</ets> ant:
cf. F. <ets>formication</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A sensation
resembling that made by the creeping of ants on the skin.</def>
<rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Formicid</ent>⟦br⟧
